\example{
Performing a matrix multiplication #{A \cdot B} for #{A \in \mathbb{R}^{(B \times D)}} and #{B \in \mathbb{R}^{(D \times K)}}, requires #{2 \times B \times D \times K} [FLOPS](4K5H)}
}
\section{Optimizers}{
\p{I hope to do a formal blog touring optimizers because I have written a paper on deep learning optimizers for my [optimization course](0033). Due to this, I will leave this blank for now. A brief list of the covered concepts are below:}
%TODO: link to optimizer blog when finished
\ul{
  \li{momentum}
